@node intro
@{b}
Introduction
@{ub}
This is my first collection of Worms levels (me being @{"Chris Spicer" link about_me}).
Having seen some of the Worms discs, I was dissappointed by their content;
they only contained five-or-so levels, and no matter how good they were that
doesn't seem like many to me.

I decided to put loadsa levels together on one disc, which is why you'll
find a massive @{b}23@{ub} levels on this disc! Incredible, I know!
@endnode
@node using
@{b}
Using this disc
@{ub}
Well, you could just load up Worms and use the levels straight from this 
floppy. Alternatively, if you have a hard drive you could transfer my levels
into the custom_levels drawer of your Worms directory. It's your choice!
@endnode
