@node metal
@{b}
Metal
@{ub}
Another training ground for young Worms, this time to see how well they 
perform on slippy surfaces. This imposing yet friction-free metal edifice
calls for self-control, excellent marksmanship (or markswormship) and a
degree of intestinal fortitude...

(See also @{"Toyland" link toyland} and @{"Flat" link flat})
@endnode
