@node domain
@{b}
Amiga Survivor
@{ub}
The Domain is a fanzine written by a few Amiga enthusiasts (myself
included) which is dedicated to the Amiga games scene. It is released
monthly and includes an astonishingly up-to-date news section
(we've beaten the glossies to some exclusives), special articles, previews,
reviews, the hottest new Amiga-based cartoon strip around (by myself, I
might add) and text stories from respected writer Andy Campbell.

Prices differ depending on where you live, so for more details, write to
the editor, Robert Iveson, at:

Amiga Survivor
